Simulation by COPASI

Simulation by COPASI

To setup COPASI to use with CellDesigner

Visit the Copasi web site.

Download the Language Binding for Java (e.g. copasi_java_win32_buildxx.zip for Windows 32bit).

Extract the downloaded file.

In the extracted folder, find

CopasiJava.dll for Windows

libCopasiJava.jnilib for MacOS X

libCopasiJava.so for Linux.

Copy the file into the CellDesigner's root folder.
